	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001060_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Hadley Green</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">10<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> July</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>Shaw</persName></p>
<lb/><p><choice><reg>T</reg><orig>t</orig></choice>he little girls' 
<lb/>eyes having become 
<lb/>worse from a 
<lb/>slight cold I send 
<lb/>her to <persName>Lawrence</persName>
<lb/>if you will 
<lb/>kindly take her 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001060_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'--> 
<lb/>I have given her 
<lb/>a little of the 
<lb/>tincture of the 
<lb/>muriate of iron 
<lb/>&amp; applied a 
<lb/>Colly<hi rend="sup">m</hi> of nitrate 
<lb/>of silver 1 1/2 gr to 
<lb/>the ounce of water 
<lb/>that<reg>'</reg>s all I have 
<lb/>done - complains of weariness 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001060_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'--> 
<lb/>&amp; headache - probably 
<lb/>effects of quick 
<lb/>growth. Her 
<lb/>mother will 
<lb/>answer any other 
<lb/>questions.</p>
<lb/><p>Will you introduce 
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="sup">rs </hi>L</persName> to <persName>Stanford</persName>
<lb/>or get some 
<lb/>envelopes for 
<lb/>her - stamped 
<lb/>&amp; gummed. 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001060_0004"/><!--pb/@n='2v'--> 
<lb/>I shall come tomorrow 
<lb/>to the Physicians 
<lb/>shall I call at 
<lb/>Lawrence's for 
<lb/>you or at the 
<lb/>R.G.S. <persName>Milne</persName> wants to present 
<lb/>a book on <placeName>China</placeName>
<lb/>to the Soc. I say 
<lb/>yes to him. </p>
<lb/><p rend="center">Ever Yours </p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><persName>D Livingstone</persName></p>
<lb/><p>I am going to <placeName>Exeter Hall</placeName>
<lb/>on Sunday </p>
			
